<p><span><strong>厦门通报病例详情</strong></span></p>
<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><strong>一、境外输入疫情</strong></span></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
<div class="lookall-shadow"></div>
